    SELECT [u].[Id], [u].[Email], [u].[FirstName], [u].[IsActive], [u].[LastName], [u].[Password], [u].[RefreshToken], [u].[RefreshTokenExpiryTime], [u].[RoleId], [u].[Token], [u].[Username]
    FROM [Users] AS [u]
    ORDER BY [u].[Username]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]

ORDER BY [t].[Username]
